                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, M</hi> 44). I took George Smith—Edward was as close to him as he is now—I had seen them together before, in High-Street, Borough, and then in Bermondsey-street—I saw Edward take some<lb></lb>thing off a table, but was not close enough to see what—the third man escaped.</p>
